from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dt2d, udf_dt2t

from pyspark.sql.types import StringType, DoubleType

from keras.callbacks import Callback
from keras.models import Sequential
from keras.layers import Dense, LSTM, Activation, TimeDistributed
from keras.utils import np_utils
from keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping

import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

udf_il_scaler = udf(lambda v: v / 100000, DoubleType())
udf_sz_scaler = udf(lambda v: v / 100, DoubleType())
udf_ct_scaler = udf(lambda v: v / 1000, DoubleType())

%pyspark

ds = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/casa_srs.parquet')\

spdf_illum = ds.select('illum').where('date = "2019-10-09"')

spdf_dataset = spdf_illum.withColumn('illum', udf(lambda s: s / illum_max, DoubleType())('illum'))

pdf_train = spdf_dataset.toPandas()
